manifest_analysis.title:
Application Data can be Backed up
[android:allowBackup=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: This flag allows anyone to backup your application data via adb. It allows users who have enabled USB debugging to copy application data off of the device.
manifest_analysis.name: Application Data can be Backed up [android:allowBackup=true]

manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.google.android.play.core.missingsplits.PlayCoreMissingSplitsActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.
manifest_analysis.name: Launch Mode of Activity is not standard.

playstore_details.title: Coins Wallet for bitcoin and litecoin
playstore_details.description:
This wallet helps people to create bitcoin or litecoin transactions
with 0 (zero) blockchain fee. Yes, you send cash absolutely free.
This is free secure wallet, all in one: cold storage, purchasing Bitcoins and  Litecoins with bank card, instant exchange, withdrawing cryptocurrency to bank card and more.
--Features--
All bitcoin and litecoin transactions are completely anonymous.
Complete anonymity - we do not collect your personal data.
All your money are protected by biometric lock.
All your funds are secured with heavy data encryption.
Build in QR codes scanner, helps enter destination bitcoin or litecoin address.
At any time you can disable the app remotely if your phone lost.
Easy to check out your funds balance and all transactions.
Send BTC or LTC with no fees or pay a small fee for faster delivery.
App shows prices in any fiat currency, which you select.
Exchange bitcoins and litecoins.
Purchasing and withdrawing cryptocurrency with bank card.
Good oportunity to gain from your funds. Deposit your bitcoins or litecoins for a fixed term at good interest rate.

--Security--
Access your money securely anywhere, anytime. You are not losing your bitcoins and litecoins even if you lose your device.
Bank grade encryption and password hashing to protect your funds.

App has built-in exchange with best exchange rates which are on market. This exchange feature is instant and does not require any identification, and does not ask you for any personal data, allowing you to remain anonymous.

--Support--
We value our relationship with our customers and strive to provide you with assistance and answers when you need it. Our support team is available to answer any questions or concerns that you may have.
